When copying the content of Code Block Macro from Confluence out to the Text Editor (WordPad, Notepad), it will lose the line break and indentation that's applied in Code Block Macro.

*Steps to reproduce*
# Create a code macro containing this:
{code}
PROCEDURE sendMail
        ( pRecipient VARCHAR2
        , pSubject   VARCHAR2
        , pMessage   VARCHAR2 );
{code}
# Save the page
# Copy the contents of Code Block Macro
# Paste it in WordPad:
{panel}
PROCEDURE sendMail
( pRecipient VARCHAR2
, pSubject VARCHAR2
, pMessage VARCHAR2 );
{panel}
# Paste it in Notepad:
{panel}
PROCEDURE sendMail        ( pRecipient VARCHAR2        , pSubject   VARCHAR2        , pMessage   VARCHAR2 );
{panel}

